sourcesContent:
let timelineElements = [
    {
      id: 1,
      title: "Idea Conception",
      description:
        "Came up with the idea, created a design, and began working on functionality. Original design focused on cognitive behavioral therapy (CBT) exercisses, and the creation of sharable PDF files.",
      date: "December 2020",
      icon: "work",
    },
    {
      id: 2,
      title: "Information Gathering",
      description:
        "Reached out to professionals in the field of psychology for volunteer help. Researched academic informat on CBT techniques to gain additional insight. Created prototypes for individual features.",
      date: "January 2021",
      icon: "school",
    },
    {
      id: 3,
      title: "Design",
      description:
        "Conceptualized the apps visual design. Created the XML layout files and app icons.",
      date: "February 2021",
      icon: "work",
    },
    {
      id: 4,
      title: "Feature Rework",
      description:
        "Changed apps functionality to center around an online database and analysis of user data, rather than PDF creation.",
      date: "March 2021",
      icon: "work",
    },
    {
      id: 5,
      title: "Finished Worksheets",
      description:
        "Completed the functionality of the CBT based exercises.",
      date: "April 2021",
      icon: "work",
    },
    {
        id: 6,
        title: "Finished Data Analysis",
        description:
          "Completed the functionality of the data analysis portion from the users worksheet data.",
        date: "May 2021",
        icon: "work",
      },

      {
        id: 7,
        title: "Preparation for Launch",
        description:
          "Fixing bugs testing, and modifying the app to meet the Play Store requirements.",
        date: "May 2021",
        icon: "work",
      },
  ];
  
  export default timelineElements;
